No worries! Thanks for jumping on this quickly

Sure thing! This is the weird thing with jenkins, it's almost entirely side-effects all the way down the stack :joy:
Trying to run them in parallel is tricky so I've been keeping an eye out :smile:

Ok those are both running fresh now
I'll announce the 'fix' to handle in case anyone else's PRs were mis-status'd thus :slightly_smiling_face:
